metadata.name: METAPHS #01
metadata.description:
“METAMORPHOSIS” 
No other than the simple circle of life.

A photographic serie of elements in a real state of decomposition that seeks to manifest THAT specific instance of energy transmutation where the death of a living organism gives birth of a new one.

There are no endings without new beginnings.  As in life, everything transforms again and again in an endless spiral.

“Where one world dies, another is born.” 

Join the spiral!
